                  </hi>. I am in the service of a pawnbroker. I produce a sheet pawned by a woman on the 9th of Jan., in the name of Ann Johnson.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> This woman persuaded me to leave my friends, and go to live with her; she is only a brother keeper.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430227-name-855" type="witnessName">
