                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I never kept such a house in my life—I keep a respectable house—the prisoner came to me and said she had been keeping her father's house, and had left him—she begged I would give her a night's lodging—I never suffer men and women to come to my house.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Witness for the Defence.</hi>
               </p>
